### Makes slides 2.5x faster, to match a max level Snowdrift Artifact's slide speed. Infinite Slide mod is recommended.
### BE CAREFUL! This also affects forced slides, so YOU WILL DIE to Graveward's forced slide if you're not ready for it!

SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Operative/_Shared/_Design/Character/BPChar_Operative.Default__BPChar_Operative_C,Att_SlideSpeedMultiplier,0,,(Value=1.8,BaseValue=1.8)
SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Gunner/_Shared/_Design/Character/BPChar_Gunner.Default__BPChar_Gunner_C,Att_SlideSpeedMultiplier,0,,(Value=1.8,BaseValue=1.8)
SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/SirenBrawler/_Shared/_Design/Character/BPChar_Siren.Default__BPChar_Siren_C,Att_SlideSpeedMultiplier,0,,(Value=1.8,BaseValue=1.8)
SparkPatchEntry,(1,1,0,),/Game/PlayerCharacters/Beastmaster/_Shared/_Design/Character/BPChar_Beastmaster.Default__BPChar_Beastmaster_C,Att_SlideSpeedMultiplier,0,,(Value=1.8,BaseValue=1.8)
